Multi-Arch: foreign
Recommends: openssh-client
Suggests: docker
Description: Daemon for infrastructure continuous SCAP compliance check
 This service is a daemon that allow periodic compliance scans of a complete
 infrastructure, supporting local check, remote check, VM or Docker check.
 The daemon is associated to a CLI allowing easy configuration of targets and
 security profiles to evaluate and easy results and reports management
